{"id":74,"ayahs":[{"number":181,"arabic":"لَّقَدْ سَمِعَ ٱللَّهُ قَوْلَ ٱلَّذِينَ قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ فَقِيرٌۭ وَنَحْنُ أَغْنِيَآءُ ۘ سَنَكْتُبُ مَا قَالُوا۟ وَقَتْلَهُمُ ٱلْأَنۢبِيَآءَ بِغَيْرِ حَقٍّۢ وَنَقُولُ ذُوقُوا۟ عَذَابَ ٱلْحَرِيقِ","translation":"God has indeed heard the saying of those who said, \"Behold, God is poor while we are rich!\" We shall record what they have said, as well as their slaying of prophets against all right, and We shall say [unto them on Judgment Day]: \"Taste suffering through fire","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/474.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":83865,"position":1,"arabic":"لَّقَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83866,"position":2,"arabic":"سَمِعَ","translation":"শুনেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83867,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83868,"position":4,"arabic":"قَوْلَ","translation":"(তাদের) কথা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83869,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83870,"position":6,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83871,"position":7,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"''নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83872,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83873,"position":9,"arabic":"فَقِيرٌۭ","translation":"দরিদ্র","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83874,"position":10,"arabic":"وَنَحْنُ","translation":"আর আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83875,"position":11,"arabic":"أَغْنِيَآءُ ۘ","translation":"ধনী''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83877,"position":12,"arabic":"سَنَكْتُبُ","translation":"আমরা লিখে রাখবো","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83878,"position":13,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83879,"position":14,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83880,"position":15,"arabic":"وَقَتْلَهُمُ","translation":"ও তাদের হত্যা করা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83881,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنۢبِيَآءَ","translation":"নবীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83882,"position":17,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ব্যাতিত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83883,"position":18,"arabic":"حَقٍّۢ","translation":"ন্যায়ভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83884,"position":19,"arabic":"وَنَقُولُ","translation":"এবং আমরা বলব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83885,"position":20,"arabic":"ذُوقُوا۟","translation":"''তোমরা স্বাদ নাও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83886,"position":21,"arabic":"عَذَابَ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83887,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱلْحَرِيقِ","translation":"দহনের''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_181_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83888,"position":23,"arabic":"١٨١","translation":"(১৮১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":182,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ بِمَا قَدَّمَتْ أَيْدِيكُمْ وَأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ لَيْسَ بِظَلَّامٍۢ لِّلْعَبِيدِ","translation":"in return for what your own hands have wrought - for never does God do the least wrong to His creatures!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/475.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":83961,"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83962,"position":2,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"একারণে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83963,"position":3,"arabic":"قَدَّمَتْ","translation":"আগে পাঠিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83964,"position":4,"arabic":"أَيْدِيكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের হাত (অর্থাৎ) কৃতকর্ম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83965,"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83966,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83967,"position":7,"arabic":"لَيْسَ","translation":"নন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83968,"position":8,"arabic":"بِظَلَّامٍۢ","translation":"জুলুমকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83969,"position":9,"arabic":"لِّلْعَبِيدِ","translation":"বান্দাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_182_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83970,"position":10,"arabic":"١٨٢","translation":"(১৮২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":183,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ عَهِدَ إِلَيْنَآ أَلَّا نُؤْمِنَ لِرَسُولٍ حَتَّىٰ يَأْتِيَنَا بِقُرْبَانٍۢ تَأْكُلُهُ ٱلنَّارُ ۗ قُلْ قَدْ جَآءَكُمْ رُسُلٌۭ مِّن قَبْلِى بِٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ وَبِٱلَّذِى قُلْتُمْ فَلِمَ قَتَلْتُمُوهُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","translation":"As for those who maintain, \"Behold, God has bidden us not to believe in any apostle unless he comes unto us with burnt offerings\" - say [unto them, O Prophet]: \"Even before me there came unto you apostles with all evidence of the truth, and with that whereof you speak: why, then, did you slay them, if what you say is true?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/476.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":83986,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83987,"position":2,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83988,"position":3,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"''নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83989,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83990,"position":5,"arabic":"عَهِدَ","translation":"নির্দেশ দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83991,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَيْنَآ","translation":"আমাদের প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83992,"position":7,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83993,"position":8,"arabic":"نُؤْمِنَ","translation":"আমরা ঈমান আনব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83994,"position":9,"arabic":"لِرَسُولٍ","translation":"কোন রাসূলের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83995,"position":10,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","translation":"যতক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83996,"position":11,"arabic":"يَأْتِيَنَا","translation":"আমাদের কাছে নিয়ে আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83997,"position":12,"arabic":"بِقُرْبَانٍۢ","translation":"এক কুরবানী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83998,"position":13,"arabic":"تَأْكُلُهُ","translation":"তা খেয়ে ফেলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83999,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارُ ۗ","translation":"(অদৃশ্যের) আগুন''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84001,"position":15,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84002,"position":16,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"''নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84003,"position":17,"arabic":"جَآءَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের কাছে এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84004,"position":18,"arabic":"رُسُلٌۭ","translation":"অনেক রাসূল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84005,"position":19,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84006,"position":20,"arabic":"قَبْلِى","translation":"আমার পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84007,"position":21,"arabic":"بِٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ","translation":"উজ্জ্বল নিদর্শন সহকারে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84008,"position":22,"arabic":"وَبِٱلَّذِى","translation":"এবং ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84009,"position":23,"arabic":"قُلْتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা বলেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84010,"position":24,"arabic":"فَلِمَ","translation":"তবে কেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84011,"position":25,"arabic":"قَتَلْتُمُوهُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হত্যা করেছ তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84012,"position":26,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84013,"position":27,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84014,"position":28,"arabic":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যবাদী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_183_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84015,"position":29,"arabic":"١٨٣","translation":"(১৮৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":184,"arabic":"فَإِن كَذَّبُوكَ فَقَدْ كُذِّبَ رُسُلٌۭ مِّن قَبْلِكَ جَآءُو بِٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ وَٱلزُّبُرِ وَٱلْكِتَٰبِ ٱلْمُنِيرِ","translation":"And if they give thee the lie - even so, before thy time, have [other] apostles been given the lie when they came with all evidence of the truth, and with books of divine wisdom, and with light-giving revelation.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/477.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":84053,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"যদি তবুও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84054,"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَّبُوكَ","translation":"তোমাকে অস্বীকার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84055,"position":3,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","translation":"তবে (নতুন কিছু নয়)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84056,"position":4,"arabic":"كُذِّبَ","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84057,"position":5,"arabic":"رُسُلٌۭ","translation":"রাসূলদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84058,"position":6,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84059,"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلِكَ","translation":"তোমার পূর্বেও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84060,"position":8,"arabic":"جَآءُو","translation":"তারা এসেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84061,"position":9,"arabic":"بِٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ","translation":"সুস্পষ্ট নিদর্শনসহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84062,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱلزُّبُرِ","translation":"ও (অনেক) সহীফা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84063,"position":11,"arabic":"وَٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"ও কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84064,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنِيرِ","translation":"আলোকদানকারী (সাথে নিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_184_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84065,"position":13,"arabic":"١٨٤","translation":"(১৮৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":185,"arabic":"كُلُّ نَفْسٍۢ ذَآئِقَةُ ٱلْمَوْتِ ۗ وَإِنَّمَا تُوَفَّوْنَ أُجُورَكُمْ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ ۖ فَمَن زُحْزِحَ عَنِ ٱلنَّارِ وَأُدْخِلَ ٱلْجَنَّةَ فَقَدْ فَازَ ۗ وَمَا ٱلْحَيَوٰةُ ٱلدُّنْيَآ إِلَّا مَتَٰعُ ٱلْغُرُورِ","translation":"Every human being is bound to taste death: but only on the Day of Resurrection will you be requited in full [for whatever you have done] - whereupon he that shall be drawn away from the fire and brought into paradise will indeed have gained a triumph: for the life of this world is nothing but an enjoyment of self-delusion.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/478.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":84104,"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84105,"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْسٍۢ","translation":"ব্যক্তিই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84106,"position":3,"arabic":"ذَآئِقَةُ","translation":"স্বাদ গ্রহণকারী (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84107,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتِ ۗ","translation":"মৃত্যুর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84109,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِنَّمَا","translation":"এবং প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84110,"position":6,"arabic":"تُوَفَّوْنَ","translation":"তোমাদের পূর্ণ দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84111,"position":7,"arabic":"أُجُورَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের পুরস্কার সমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84112,"position":8,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84113,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ ۖ","translation":"কিয়ামাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84115,"position":10,"arabic":"فَمَن","translation":"অতঃপর যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84116,"position":11,"arabic":"زُحْزِحَ","translation":"রক্ষা করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84117,"position":12,"arabic":"عَنِ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_185_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":84118,"position":13,"arabic":